eg?resize=1024%2C682&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/pexels-photo-2085832.jpeg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/pexels-photo-2085832.jpeg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/pexels-photo-2085832.jpeg?w=1880&amp;ssl=1 1880w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/pexels-photo-2085832.jpeg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Photo by LJ on <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pexels.com\/photo\/shallow-focus-photo-of-r2-d2-figure-2085832\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pexels.com<\/a><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"investing-sensibly-according-to-ai-chat-gpt\"><strong>Investing Sensibly According to AI ChatGPT<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Investing your money wisely can be a daunting task, especially for those who are new to the world of finance. However, with the right guidance and a little bit of research, anyone can become a savvy investor. In this article, we will outline some key principles of sensible investing to help you get started.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Start early: Time is one of the most valuable assets in investing. The earlier you start, the more time your investments have to grow and compound. This means that even small contributions made early in life can grow into substantial savings over time. So, if you haven&#8217;t started investing yet, now is the time to get started.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Diversify your investments: Diversification is a crucial part of any investment strategy. This means spreading your investments across different types of assets, such as stocks, bonds, and real estate. By doing so, you can reduce your overall risk and increase the likelihood of earning consistent returns over time.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Be patient: Investing is a long-term game, and it&#8217;s important to remember that short-term fluctuations in the market are normal. It&#8217;s important to avoid making impulsive decisions based on short-term market movements, and instead focus on your long-term goals and investment strategy.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keep an eye on fees: Fees can eat into your investment returns, so it&#8217;s important to be mindful of the fees you&#8217;re paying. Make sure to review all of the fees associated with your investments, including investment management fees, trading fees, and administrative fees. By keeping an eye on fees, you can ensure that your investments are working as hard as possible for you.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Educate yourself: The more you know about investing, the better equipped you will be to make informed decisions. Take the time to educate yourself on the different types of investments, the stock market, and basic financial concepts. Read books, attend seminars, and speak with financial advisors to help you make informed decisions.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>In conclusion, sensible investing requires patience, dedication, and a long-term outlook. By following these key principles, you can create a strong investment portfolio that will help you reach your financial goals. Remember, investing is a marathon, not a sprint, so take the time to do your research and make informed decisions. With the right approach, you can build a secure financial future for yourself and your family.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your Faithful Friend,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>ChatGPT<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"microsoft-stock\"><strong>Microsoft Stock<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This little experiment with ChatGPT and <a href=\"http:\/\/198.199.80.40\/2023\/02\/building-wealth-a-robot-wealth\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"1004\" target=\"_blank\">artificial intelligence<\/a> certainly is making me want to add to my existing Microsoft position among other AI stocks. Time will tell how this all plays out, but hopefully we are not at the beginning stages of self destruction akin to The Matrix movies.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"thoughts\"><strong>Thoughts?<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Please share your thoughts about our future world with ChatGPT and AI. Are we doomed or will this enhance the lives of millions and billions of people?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>ChatGPT Wrote us an article about Investing. Here&#8217;s what AI told us to do.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":14337,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"jetpack_post_was_ever_published":false,"_jetpack_newsletter_access":"","_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id":0,"footnotes":"","jetpack_publicize_message":"","jetpack_is_tweetstorm":false,"jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled":true,"jetpack_social_post_already_shared":false,"jetpack_social_options":{"image_generator_settings":{"template":"highway","enabled":false}}},"categories":[16,21,23],"tags":[995,994],"jetpack_publicize_connections":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/chatgpt-e1676490296901.jpeg?fit=533%2C800&ssl=1","jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":16665,"url":"https:\/\/truewealth.moneyvikings.com\/2023\/08\/make-money-using-chatgpt-the-barbie-way\/","url_meta":{"origin":14336,"position":0},"title":"Make Money Using ChatGPT (the Barbie Way?)","author":"greg","date":"August 26, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Everyone I know that saw the Barbie movie loved it. Barbie and her friends practiced all kinds of professions over the years and still do to this day. And every profession has its tools, skill sets and knowledge. If you are offering your services to others, you will need specific\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Technology&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Technology","link"